snippet.title: MixMob: Racer 1 Is Coming – Are You Ready to Dominate?
snippet.description:
Racing games lack strategy. Card games are slow. MixMob: Racer 1 changes the game.

🏁 Fast, skill-based card racing
😤 3-minute real-time battles
🏆 Climb the ranks, win big

🔥 This was Beta. Now imagine what’s coming next. 👀

Who’s ready?
